surfacevel2strain/README

Code for a a spherical-wavelet-based estimation of velocity fields on the sphere from discrete 3-component (or 2-component) GPS observations.

Step 1:
link your directory with GPS data files to the base directory:
  rm gps_data
  ln -s YOUR_GPS_DATA_DIR gps_data

Step 2:
check out the documentation in USER_INFO

Directories:
  gmt           -- Perl scripts for plotting in GMT
  gps_data      -- link to original and modified GPS data files
  matlab        -- primary matlab codes (surfacevel2strain.m)
  matlab_output -- output files from matlab
  USER_INFO     -- PDF notes and documentation

-----------------------------------------------
